{"tid":2078360,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中環新海濱商業地以「雙信封」招標 料地價400多億","createTime":"2020-06-25T03:57:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-25T04:31:20.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2932124a17e361cb211219c442f8e7756b0f92","tid":2078360,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T03:57:24.000Z","msg":"中環新海濱商業地以「雙信封」招標 料地價400多億<br />\n2020-06-25 HKT 09:40<br />\n<br />\n新一季賣地計劃預料日內公布，市場預料有機會推出中環新海濱三號用地。當局早前預告，這幅商業地會以「雙信封」方式招標出售，會考慮投標者提出的價格與設計建議。<br />\n<br />\n發展局早前在海濱事務委員會表示，設計和價格比重將各佔一半，當局會成立標書評審委員會，由政府人員負責評分會邀請專業人士提供意見，地皮會設有底價。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534027-20200625.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534027-20200625.htm&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfdDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=034592f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1534027-20200625.htm&h=67708e66\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1534027-20200625.htm</a>"},{"pid":"e1e28b6703b67c97cf34d2bcc0f420a642f6ddcc","tid":2078360,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:05:30.000Z","msg":"呢度起樓既話會唔會五萬蚊呎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"585ee781d4452ddc3e1aa2eefb31459fec49cb7e","tid":2078360,"uid":185652,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"紅底資金+中國建築 is 100%<br />\n連4大家族都唔會bid 到"},{"pid":"8df2e23cbf19e35e513dbdac172194d23b2889d7","tid":2078360,"uid":85629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f810ea12832f313b762bbcf5030e4669cf5a1d6d","tid":2078360,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-25T04:26:59.000Z","msg":"專